---
title: Beef Tenderloin with Mushroom Sauce with Roasted Brussels Sprouts & Couscous
description: This luxurious dish is bursting with umami. Not sure if you’ve ever experienced the “fifth taste?” After one bite, you’ll totally understand the obsession. Melt-in-your-mouth beef tenderloin is seared to perfection, then draped in a supremely savory mushroom sauce. It’s served alongside crispy roasted Brussels sprouts, plus couscous tossed with a decadent garlic herb butter. Don’t be surprised if you mistake your dinner table for the fancy corner booth at that steakhouse downtown.
